data.title: The administrative divisions of Serbia - Map (districts of Serbia)
data.meta_description: List names of twenty-nine districts of the Republic of Serbia or their administrative centers, as well as the name of capital city.
data.text:
Thank you for your nice comment :) As far as I know there is only one correct name for the Belgrade city in English, but you inspired me to make a Serbian version of this quiz with the name "Београд" ;)

Please let me know if everything that I wrote there is correct, because Serbian is not my native language:

https://www.jetpunk.com/user-quizzes/1333764/quiz-2

Since Serbia is using two types of alphabet I think it would be cool if this quiz accepted also Latin script, so maybe this will be the next change I will apply.
